

STEP 1: Build Docker image
docker build -t my-js-app .
docker images

STEP 2: Run locally (test first)
docker run -p 3000:3000 my-js-app


STEP 3: Login to Docker Hub
docker login



STEP 4: Tag the image for Docker Hub

Format:

docker tag <local-image> <dockerhub-username>/<repo-name>:<tag>
Example:

docker tag my-js-app elktraining/my-js-app:v1


docker images


STEO 5: Push image to Docker Hub

docker push elktraining/my-js-app:v1
